{
  "text": "To generate single-cell and neuroblast clones in the MB, we used the mosaic analysis with a repressible cell marker (MARCM) technique [CITATION_1] FRT80B, hsFLP/\u03e9; FRT80B, pupae were heat-shocked at 37\u00b0C for 30 min at 50 h after puparium formation. For neuroblast clones, first instar larvae of the same genotypes were heat-shocked at 37\u00b0C for 30 min. The morphology of the MB clones was analyzed in flies 3-7 d old.",
